title: Eddie Checks In After His Walk + Bobby’s Top 5 Country Summer Songs + Amy Gets An IG Medical Diagnosis
itunes:title: Eddie Checks In After His Walk + Bobby’s Top 5 Country Summer Songs + Amy Gets An IG Medical Diagnosis
description:
We talk to Eddie with an update on how he’s feeling at home after his walk from this week. We also find out the crazy amount of money he raised in total! Bobby shares his Top 5 Country songs of the summer. Amy shares the story of how listeners diagnosed something after seeing it on her Instagram and why she is very thankful.
